{"tid":1238862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家對各有各做既理解係點?","createTime":"2019-06-18T03:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T04:53:31.000Z","uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"365a9fb95a1b42b9de53134e8d3058de83a58ce9","tid":1238862,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:24:46.000Z","msg":"我既理解係，現時有兩大派系 1: 和理非 2: 武勇派。以每個派系作為一個個體，每個個體既行動不互相批評、干預等等，並係需要時提供支援，大家取長補短。每個派系應係行動前取得共識，而非以個人或者圍內十幾人既想法而去做。<br />\n<br />\n尤其武勇派無領頭人，做事好多時都要靠自發，而且同時亦係面對最高風險，如果行動前無取得大部份人共識而去做，想法既不同好容易做成分裂或者指責，而且因為人數不夠多，風險亦比平常高好多。<span style=\"color: red;\">所以最好派系間統一意見，然後齊上齊落</span>。"},{"pid":"70a9bf44e9d01d261b20611c229543b5214f5456","tid":1238862,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f3ad7ca02de7c98cb7d227c29ccac7cfd358b2","tid":1238862,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ad95066f8fc3f89fc442c7a47ecf199ee7b043","tid":1238862,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}